This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with building a chat system that generates intelligent responses in a conversation. It also involves the use of neural network models for natural language processing. 

It could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as the paper involves the development of an intelligent chat system. 

cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another likely sub-category as the paper uses a neural network model to capture features from the current and previous utterances to facilitate the formation of relevant responses. 

cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is also a possible sub-category as the paper involves the use of neural network models. 

Finally, cs.SD (Software Engineering) could be a potential sub-category as the paper involves the development of a software system for chatbot technology.
